desc_long							评测						“I had a hard time pulling myself away from this title. The combination of ‘just-one-more,’ the soundtrack, and the precise controls make this a sleeper hit.”Subaltern Gaming“Super Star Path nails the mixing of space shooter, roguelike, and puzzle genres in a way I didn't even know I wanted.”Destructoid“Super Star Path puts you in a top-down alley choked with enemies practically begging to get shot down, but you've got to carefully decide what you're going to blow away.”IndieGames													Bot Vice, our new game!									http://store.steampowered.com/app/491040																						关于这款游戏							Classic color match puzzle meets space shoot'em up action! Hop into your spaceship, open a path through huge waves of aliens and other hazards, and face intense boss battles!Randomized puzzle stages.Intense boss fights.Unlock, buy and upgrade new ships.Boss Rush mode.Colorful 16-bit style graphics.Arcade-like FM synth soundtrack.Gamepad support.DEFAULT CONTROLSIMPORTANT!It's more puzzle than shoot'em up, in fact, all shooting action is condensed in the boss fights!It's short. It's an arcade! You can get 100% completion in 1.5 hours if you're good enough.CONTACTForums: Steam DiscussionsWebsite: http://dyagames.comTwitter: @DYAGames						
